James Kenneth Robinson, born: 14 5mo 1916; Frederick Co. VA; died: 8 4mo 1990; Winchester, VA; buried: Mount Hebron Cem., Winchester, VA; See his Find A Grave entry.

Kenneth, married: 4 2mo 1937; Danbury, Danbury Twp, Stokes Co. NC; June Estelle Bean, divorced;

J. Kenneth was a fruit grower & orchardist in Frederick County. He was a member of the Virginia Senate from the 21st district from 12 1mo 1966 to 3 1mo 1971 and then a member of the U.S. House of Representatives from Virginia's 7th district from 3 1mo 1971 to 3 1mo 1985. He was highly regarded in Winchester, Frederick County & statewide for his service.

See the Wikipedia bio for J. Kenneth Robinson.

See the Group Photos at Centre Meeting.

Issue: Robinson

